                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina providente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. [Reg]alem decet exellentiam sanctis ac
                        venerabilibus locis ex suis largiri, et largita confirmare ac sub
                        defensionis munimine cuncta corroborare. Quapropter omnium sancte Dei
                        Aecclesie fidelium nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum comper[ia]t
                        sollertia, qualiter peticione et interventu <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Bishops" ref="#people/1521">Sigefredi</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1420"><placeName
                                ref="#places/53">Parmensis</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> atque <persName key="#Intercessory #Count"
                                ><name ref="Elisardus">Elisiardi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> beato Siro sacerrimo confessori sueque
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/220"
                            key="#Parchment_documents #Islands #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Mills #Ports #Bridges/pontoons #Plebs #Public_exactions #Tolls #Teloneum #Immunity #Inquisitio #Churches #Baptismal_churches #Monasteries #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            >sancte <placeName ref="#places/65">Ticinensi</placeName>
                            aecclesiae</orgName>, cui <persName key="#Bishops"><name
                                ref="Liutfredus">Liutefredus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">presul</rs> preesse videtur, omnes res et familias, <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">abbatias</rs> videlicet, [<rs
                            key="#Plebs #Baptismal_churches">plebes</rs>] et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >cortes</rs> cunctaque quae ad eandem Ticinensem aecclesiam pertinere
                        vel respicere videbantur eo tempore quo eadem Ticinensis civitas caelitus
                        furore misso consumpta est, per hoc nostrum preceptum concedimus, largimur,
                        confirmamus et corroboramus; nominative videlicet, <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >abbatiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            >in honore Domini Salvatoris</orgName> in campania non longe a <rs
                            key="#Rivers">Ticino</rs> sitam, <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1465">Sanctaeque Mariae ad Perticam</orgName> et
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1466">Sancti Michaelis quae dicitur
                            Maior</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            >Sanctique Romuli</orgName>, et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            >Sancte Cristine</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1467">Sancteque Mustiole</orgName>, omnesque <rs
                            key="#Churches">cardinales capellas</rs> tam extra quam infra urbem
                        positas, nec non <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1468">Vetus</orgName> et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity #Monasteries"
                            >Anzonis et Sigemarii</orgName> et unum <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs> in <placeName ref="#places/2782" key="#Monasteries"
                            >Cariade</placeName>, <rs key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> eciam <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2386"><placeName ref="#places/2783" key="#Curtes"
                                >Cecim[a]m</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2387">Montem Velleris</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2388"><placeName ref="#places/2784" key="#Curtes"
                                >Summi</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2389"><placeName ref="#places/2785" key="#Curtes"
                                >Sarianum</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2390"><placeName ref="#places/480" key="#Curtes"
                                >Robuscallam</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2391">Robuscaletam</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/268"><placeName ref="#places/578" key="#Curtes"
                                >Cugullo</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2392">Tenesi</geogName>, et super <rs key="#Lakes">lacum
                            Cumanum</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2393"><placeName ref="#places/2786" key="#Curtes"
                                >Cernobium</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2394">Menasi</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/2395"><placeName ref="#places/2787" key="#Curtes"
                                >Maximo</placeName></geogName>, quae est in <placeName
                            ref="#places/2788">Valle Tellina</placeName>, verum eciam et <rs
                            key="#Bridges/pontoons">vada</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fisheries">piscaria</rs> atque <rs key="#Ports">portus</rs>, id
                        est <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Ports #Immunity"
                            >Navicella Episcopi</geogName> et <rs key="#Ports">portum</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Ports #Immunity"
                            >[Ca]ballaricium</geogName> in <rs key="#Rivers">Ticino</rs>. Insuper
                        eciam concedimus ut a <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Ports"
                                ><placeName key="#Confinia #Ports">[portu
                            Barbi]ani</placeName></geogName> usque ad <rs key="#Ports">portum</rs>
                        qui dicitur <geogName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Ports"
                                ><placeName key="#Confinia #Ports">Burigo</placeName></geogName>, et
                        a <placeName key="#Confinia #Canals">capite Verna[u]le</placeName> usque ad
                            <placeName key="#Confinia #Bridges/pontoons">vadum Farigeni</placeName>,
                        cum <rs key="#Islands">insulis</rs> et <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscationibus</rs> et <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, cum omnibus
                        quae dici et nominari possunt infra ipsas <rs key="#Confinia">fines</rs>,
                        sint <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >in iure et po[testa]te prelibate aecclesiae</rs>; et neque <rs
                            key="#Tolls">ripaticum</rs>, neque <rs>terraticum</rs>, neque <rs
                            key="#Teloneum">teloneum</rs>, neque <rs key="#Teloneum"
                            >palificaturam</rs>, <rs key="#Immunity">neque aliquam <rs
                                key="#Public_exactions">functionem</rs> ullo in loco ad publicam
                            partem persolvat</rs>, sed cuncta, sicut iam dictum est, ante incendium
                        Ticinensis urbis undecumque aut quomodocumque eadem Ticinensis aecclesia
                        investita fuit seu per precepta a nostris precessoribus seu per quecumque
                            <rs key="#Parchment_documents">instrumenta cartarum</rs> a fidelibus
                        collata, per hoc nostrum preceptum concedimus, largimur, comfirmamus et
                        corroboramus, una cum <rs key="#Monasteries">monasteriis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">abbatiis</rs>, <rs key="#Curtes">cortibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs #Baptismal_churches">plebibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">massariciis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs>, <rs key="#Royal_aldius"
                            >aldionibus et aldianis</rs> omnibusque rebus quae dici vel nominari
                        possunt ad eandem Ticinensem aecclesiam pertinentibus in integrum.
                        Concedimus eciam ut, si ex quibuslibet rebus vel familiis prefatae
                        aecclesiae aliqua intentio horta fuerit, <rs key="#Inquisitio">per
                            inquisitionem trium bonorum hominum ex filiis eiusdem ecclesiae per
                            sacramentum confirmetur quod pars ipsius ecclesiae inde investita
                            fuerit</rs>, et sic firmiter in posterum possideat. Statuentes itaque
                        iubemus, ut <rs key="#Immunity">nullus dux, neque marchio, comes eciam,
                            vicecomes, sculdascius vel aliquis minister publicus aut aliqua persona
                            disvestire aut invadere de rebus predicte ecclesiae sine legali iudicio,
                            teloneum quoque aut ullam publicam funccionem exigere aut mansionaticum
                            presumtive accipere audeat, sed eadem ecclesia cum reb[u]s atque
                            familiis [sub] nostre nostrorumque s[u]cc[e]ssorum defensionis
                            munimin[e] per[frui a]c p[a]cifice manere queat</rs>. Si quis igitur hoc
                        nostrum preceptum violare temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras mille</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >medietatem camerae nostrae</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem vicario ips[iu]s
                            [e]cclesiae suisque successoribus</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur
                        diligenciusque ab omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo
                        nostro subter iussimus sigillari. Signa domnorum regum Hugonis (MF) (MF)
                        atque Lotharii. <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/1535"
                            >Giseprandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1531">Bosonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi (SR).</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
